## Checklist
- [ ] Diff read before author notes.
- [ ] All changed files mapped to a requirement or acceptance signal.
- [ ] Each changed file reviewed line-by-line for correctness.
- [ ] Safety scan completed for changed paths.
- [ ] Test coverage assessed for each changed function or behavior slice.
- [ ] Every blocker cites a reproducible observation.
- [ ] Remediation is actionable, not "please reconsider".
- [ ] Questions are separated from blockers.
- [ ] Bottom line is one sentence, aligned with verdict severity.
